title: 820-01700-05 Personal Machine 16” 100% Fan spin
message: So, well my personal MacBook Pro just died. I bought it a few months ago on eBay and it was working fine yesterday. While watching a YouTube livestream it just all of a sudden died and now only has full Fan Spin. You can only stop it by unplugging the charger and battery. Anyone got a clue what could be causing this? On the go atm so I only have limited diagnostics equipment....
